messages.messageBody:
Back by popular demand.........

Unschoolers' 5th Annual (Winter) Waterpark Gathering

WHEN:    January 23 - 27, 2012

WHERE:  Kalahari Indoor Waterpark Resort & Convention Center
                  Sandusky, Ohio

THEME:  CAKE!!!!

Yes, you can have your cake and eat it too!

To find out more and to help with the planning of our BIG 5th year celebration, join our UWG yahoo group at:  http://groups.yahoo.com/group/UWG/

2012 UWG Coordinators
     Carol Reinhard - Coordinator / Founder
     Kim Lowery - Main Events Coordinator
     Kimberly Conti - Speakers Coordinator
     Bethany Ward - Funshops Coordinator
     Debra Bures - Registration Coordinator

[ Please help us spread the word by passing this along to all your unschoolly friends and groups.  THANKS! ]
